Package: lsconnect
Version: 1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: network-manager, ca-certificates
Maintainer: Tyler <tylacy90@outlook.com>
Description: Easy command-line helper to connect to Lone Star College Wi-Fi
 A simple NetworkManager-based tool that configures and connects
 to Lone Star College's WPA2-Enterprise Wi-Fi network.
